{"tid":1742721,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"周一油麻地「圍魏救趙」被告：警逼讀「時代垃圾 溝渠曱甴」","createTime":"2019-11-21T01:58:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T02:33:33.000Z","uid":212626,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"3e2b46a4f6743078de83596c2fa24c9756778f91","tid":1742721,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T01:58:16.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】大批示威者周一（18日）到油麻地一帶「圍魏救趙」，營救被困理大者。60人涉於油麻地彌敦道近窩打老道暴動，昨在九龍城裁判法院提堂，案件分成3案，在晚上近7時半陸續開庭，直至晚上11時許散庭。<span style=\"color: red;\">裁判官批准所有出庭應訊的被告保釋</span>，部分人須守宵禁令或禁足令，案件均押後至明年3月再訊。<span style=\"color: red;\">其中一名18歲男生透過律師投訴，曾在警署遭恐嚇，警員要求他照紙上讀出「時代垃圾，溝渠曱甴」</span>。<br />\n<br />\n大部分被告獲准1000至5000元保釋，禁足令包括女拔萃書院至廣華醫院一帶。於澳洲就讀大學的被告梁嘉淇因在海外讀書，辯方透露他案發前不久才抵港，獲准以現金5萬元及人事10萬元保釋，其間可以離港。裁判官押後3案分別在3月4、5、11日再訊，以待警方進一步調查。<br />\n<br />\n當中3名被告投訴警方，希望法庭記錄在案。<span style=\"color: red;\">其中一名18歲男生在警署遭恐嚇，警員要求他照紙上讀出「時代垃圾，溝渠曱甴」，亦有另外兩人投訴被捕時遭警員毆打</span>。<br />\n<br />\n另外，牽涉5名介乎<span style=\"color: red;\">14至15歲中學生</span>的油麻地暴動案，昨於粉嶺裁判法院少年庭提訊。被告的家屬並不反對傳媒旁聽，有父母在庭上一臉擔憂，以毛巾拭淚。其中一名少女仍留醫，5人均獲准擔保候審。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E/article/20191121/s00001/1574274648651/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20191121%2Fs00001%2F1574274648651%2F&d=s5Gqkxkf8ApsCpMlSmcRzkYZmLIq74JPLN0FyuDKESI%3D&h=0c395d91\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20191121%2Fs00001%2F1574274648651%2F&h=02fcac35\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E/article/20191121/s00001/1574274648651/</a>"},{"pid":"7a1f578acc39ad75753c2f0a31d145b4a0720dc6","tid":1742721,"uid":194325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T02:00:04.000Z","msg":"香港金融業職工總會（香港金總）將於星期六舉行特別會員大會，以商討政治工業行動事宜。本會已根據香港金總會章，於2019年11月18日以電郵通知本會會員召開特別會員大會事宜。詳情如下：<br />\n<br />\n特別會員大會<br />\n日期：2019年11月23日<br />\n時間：下午5時至8時<br />\n地點：尖沙咀金巴利道25號長利商業大廈12樓1202室<br />\n備註：<br />\n -  請出席之會員提早15分鐘前來登記，以便準時開始。<br />\n -  會場內，除大會攝影師外，不得拍攝。<br />\n<br />\n大會開始前一小時(下午4時至5時)亦有招收會員活動。請各會員及有意者撥冗出席。如有任何查詢，請透過telegram (@HKFUnion)或面書與工會成員聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n請準會員預先填寫入會表格：<br />\n中: <a href=\"https://forms.gle/JRRvX5t488CyQVPYA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FJRRvX5t488CyQVPYA&d=s5Gqkxkf8ApsCpMlSmcRzkYZmLIq74JPLN0FyuDKESI%3D&h=0a95c900\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/JRRvX5t488CyQVPYA</a><br />\neng: <a href=\"https://forms.gle/BmdiqkhX5pBEgZDy5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FBmdiqkhX5pBEgZDy5&d=s5Gqkxkf8ApsCpMlSmcRzkYZmLIq74JPLN0FyuDKESI%3D&h=729ce277\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/BmdiqkhX5pBEgZDy5</a><br />\n<br />\n工會Facebook：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKFUnion/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKFUnion%2F&d=s5Gqkxkf8ApsCpMlSmcRzkYZmLIq74JPLN0FyuDKESI%3D&h=6d524698\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKFUnion/</a><br />\n工會Telegram channel：<a href=\"https://t.me/HKFIEGU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHKFIEGU&d=s5Gqkxkf8ApsCpMlSmcRzkYZmLIq74JPLN0FyuDKESI%3D&h=6e976396\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/HKFIEGU</a><br />\n<br />\n#特別會員大會"},{"pid":"ed98b2eaa5e100dbd546e26e95e24c8964ae1da9","tid":1742721,"uid":38204,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T02:01:43.000Z","msg":"無聊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我叫100次又代表啲咩 成日以為講完就係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b497230e82c094d14e69ad6bfe9f943b2264d846","tid":1742721,"uid":113800,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T02:03:13.000Z","msg":"要投訴一定要上庭提出<br />\n有朋友之前上完庭再提出俾人不受理"},{"pid":"6d8f5541729ace4ddaf0e6a5a9c717671ccb1138","tid":1742721,"uid":176313,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"